OL,3,CCouncil not planning legal action to
OL,4,Cstop asylum seekers being housed in
OL,5,Chotel
OL,7,FCouncil bosses in Newcastle have said
OL,8,Fthey are not planning legal action to
OL,9,Fstop asylum seekers being housed in a
OL,10,Fcity centre hotel.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday (19 August), the High Court
OL,13,Fgranted Conservative-run Epping Forest
OL,14,FDistrict Council a temporary
OL,15,Finjunction requiring that asylum
OL,16,Fseekers are no longer accommodated at
OL,17,Fa hotel in Essex from 12 September.
OL,19,FLabour ministers are now bracing for
OL,20,Fsimilar challenges from local
OL,21,Fauthorities across the country.
