OL,7,FBut Newcastle City Council has
OL,8,Fconfirmed that it will not be taking
OL,9,Fsuch a step.
OL,11,FThere have been protests and counter-
OL,12,Fdemonstrations in the city centre over
OL,13,Frecent weeks in relation to a hotel
OL,14,Fbeing used to house asylum seekers.
