OL,7,FThe council has previously confirmed
OL,8,Fit is in active talks with the Home
OL,9,FOffice to end the hotel's use as
OL,10,Fasylum seeker accommodation, with
OL,11,FNewcastle Labour leader Karen Kilgour
OL,12,Fhaving called for it to be closed down
OL,13,Fand for "national change and proper
OL,14,Finvestment" in a new system aimed at
OL,15,Fprotecting existing communities and
OL,16,Fbetter integrating asylum seekers.
OL,18,FShe said on Wednesday: "We are aware
OL,19,Fof the High Court injunction granted
OL,20,Fin Epping regarding the use of a hotel
OL,21,Fto house asylum seekers.
