OL,4,Cstop asylum seekers being housed in
OL,5,Chotel
OL,7,F"Our position remains unchanged. We
OL,8,Fstrongly oppose the use of hotels as
OL,9,Faccommodation for people seeking
OL,10,Fasylum. They are not appropriate or
OL,11,Fsustainable, either for the
OL,12,Findividuals involved or for the local
OL,13,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
