OL,3,CCouncil not planning legal action to
OL,4,Cstop asylum seekers being housed in
OL,5,Chotel
OL,7,F"As I have previously said, we are in
OL,8,Factive discussions with the Home
OL,9,FOffice around how the council can take
OL,10,Fgreater control in the placement of
OL,11,Fasylum seekers in the city, while
OL,12,Fending the use of hotels. We are
OL,13,Fconfident we can achieve this without
OL,14,Fthe need to seek an injunction.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
