OL,3,CCouncil not planning legal action to
OL,4,Cstop asylum seekers being housed in
OL,5,Chotel
OL,7,F"We recognise that people seeking
OL,8,Fasylum include families, women and
OL,9,Fchildren, many of whom have faced
OL,10,Funimaginable trauma. Newcastle has a
OL,11,Fproud history of offering sanctuary,
OL,12,Fand we stand ready to play our part `
OL,13,Fbut it must be done in a way that
OL,14,Fworks for our city and supports the
OL,15,Fdignity and wellbeing of those who
OL,16,Fcome here."
