OL,4,Cstop asylum seekers being housed in
OL,5,Chotel
OL,7,FThe Government has already pledged
OL,8,Fthat it will end the use of hotels to
OL,9,Fhouse asylum seekers, in the hope of
OL,10,Fsaving billions of pounds in taxpayer
OL,11,Fmoney.
OL,13,FSecurity Minister Dan Jarvis said on
OL,14,FWednesday that the Government was
OL,15,F"looking at a range of different
OL,16,Fcontingency options" following the
OL,17,FHigh Court ruling.
