OL,3,CCouncil not planning legal action to
OL,4,Cstop asylum seekers being housed in
OL,5,Chotel
OL,7,FHe told Times Radio: "Other local
OL,8,Fauthorities will be considering
OL,9,Fwhether they wish to act in the same
OL,10,Fway that Epping (Forest) District
OL,11,FCouncil have.
OL,13,F"I think the important point to make
OL,14,Fis that nobody really thinks that
OL,15,Fhotels are a sustainable location to
OL,16,Faccommodate asylum seekers.
OL,18,F"That's precisely why the Government
OL,19,Fhas made a commitment that, by the end
OL,20,Fof this Parliament, we would have
OL,21,Fphased out the use of them."
